@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@token = bananabananabanana
@userId = 1

### ========================================
### BASKET ENDPOINTS
### ========================================

### 1. Add product to basket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/basket
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "productId": 1,
  "quantity": 2
}

###

### 2. Add another product to basket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/basket
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": {{userId}},
  "productId": 2,
  "quantity": 1
}

###

### 3. Get user's basket (replace {userId} with actual user ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/basket/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Get basket item count for user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/basket/user/{{userId}}/count
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Update basket item quantity (replace {basketItemId} with actual basket item ID)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/basket/1?quantity=5
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Remove item from basket (replace {basketItemId} with actual basket item ID)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/basket/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 7. Clear all items from user's basket
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/basket/user/{{userId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
